[
    {
        "content": "<p>Should we redefine <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib_docs/find/alg_hom\">docs#alg_hom</a> to be <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib_docs/find/non_unital_alg_hom\">docs#non_unital_alg_hom</a>?</p>",
        "id": 263791903,
        "sender_full_name": "Yury G. Kudryashov",
        "timestamp": 1638742113
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>It seems that the latter is more general than the former (and they're equivalent in case of unital associative algebras).</p>",
        "id": 263791922,
        "sender_full_name": "Yury G. Kudryashov",
        "timestamp": 1638742161
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Why are they equivalent? Isn't e.g. <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>a</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">f(a) = 0</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.10764em;\">f</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">a</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span></span></span></span> a non-unital alg. homomorphism between unital algebras?</p>",
        "id": 263792880,
        "sender_full_name": "Reid Barton",
        "timestamp": 1638743564
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>If so we should add a <code>has_zero</code> instance</p>",
        "id": 263793164,
        "sender_full_name": "Eric Wieser",
        "timestamp": 1638743945
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>So, <code>alg_hom</code> is <code>non_unital_alg_hom</code> + <code>map_one</code>?</p>",
        "id": 263794177,
        "sender_full_name": "Yury G. Kudryashov",
        "timestamp": 1638745214
    }
]